(39, 3, 'About page part one', '<p>My 5 reminds you to take a few minutes out of the day to look after YOU.  Take five minutes to take a break from your work – to stretch, exercise, re-energise and re-focus.&#160; In a world where we are all working harder and longer, My 5 provides you with the tools and inspiration to help you do more to look after yourself whether at work and at home.&#160; Just as anti-virus software offers protection for the smooth running and health of your computer, My 5 software provides health and wellness solutions for you.</p>\r\n<p>Employers are increasingly concerned with the wellbeing of their employees and searching for ways to make a difference.  My 5 offers practical help with day to day workplace health and wellness issues via My 5 online.</p>\r\n<p>The number five has a great significance in our lives.  It’s through our five senses that we experience life.  In Eastern medicine, there are five elements (earth, fire, water, metal and wood).  The number five also represents the balance point, embodying the characteristics of health, creativity, versatility and adaptability to change.</p>', 0, '2011-09-12 06:09:43', '2012-03-05 02:10:58'),
(40, 3, 'About page part two', '<p>The My 5 program has been developed with the above characteristics in mind, combining a range of different approaches including stretching, muscle balance exercises and pressure point massage.</p>', 1, '2011-09-12 06:09:43', '2012-03-05 02:10:58'),
(41, 6, 'Symptomatics', '<p><img src="/system/images/BAhbBlsHOgZmSSItMjAxMS8xMC8yNi8yM181MV8yNV8xMDNfU3ltcHRvbWF0aWNzLmpwZwY6BkVU/Symptomatics.jpg" title="Symptomatics" alt="Symptomatics" height="308" width="637" />The Symptomatic Guide takes you straight to exercises that target the part of the body that is causing discomfort. This is designed to give you quick and easy access to the exercises, making it the ideal way for busy people to use the &#160;My 5 program.</p>', 0, '2011-09-20 02:56:12', '2012-05-20 11:33:56'),
(42, 6, 'Mini Modules', '<p><img src="/system/images/BAhbBlsHOgZmSSItMjAxMS8xMC8yNi8yM181MV81Ml81NDhfbWluaV9tb2R1bGVzLmpwZwY6BkVU/mini_modules.jpg" title="Mini Modules" alt="Mini Modules" rel="225x255" height="324" width="640" />Each Mini Module comprises a series of short exercises tailored to give you an effective sequence addressing a particular theme:</p>\r\n<ul><li>Wake Up Exercises</li>\r\n<li>Kick Start Your Day</li>\r\n<li>Work Station Workout</li>\r\n<li>Energise</li>\r\n<li>Back Care </li>\r\n<li>De-Stress\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', 1, '2011-09-20 02:57:22', '2012-05-20 11:33:56'),
(43, 6, 'Audio Programs', '<p><img src="/system/images/BAhbBlsHOgZmSSIvMjAxMS8xMC8yNi8yM181NF8yMF8xODlfYXVkaW9fcHJvZ3JhbXMuanBnBjoGRVQ/audio_programs.jpg" title="Audio Programs" alt="Audio Programs" rel="225x255" height="332" width="640" />The Audio Programs offer further techniques and strategies to help improve your wellbeing, including:</p>\r\n<ul><li>Stress Buster Exercises</li>\r\n<li>Concentration and Focus Exercises</li>\r\n<li>Eye Exercises</li>\r\n</ul>', 2, '2011-09-20 02:58:16', '2012-05-20 11:33:56'),
(44, 6, 'My EQ', '<p><img src="/system/images/BAhbBlsHOgZmSSIlMjAxMS8xMC8yNi8yM181NF80Ml8yNzhfTXlFUS5qcGcGOgZFVA/MyEQ.jpg" title="My Eq" alt="My Eq" rel="225x255" height="323" width="640" />Emotions are an integral part of how we think, reason, engage and communicate from day to day.  Emotional intelligence is a measure of how effectively we manage the interplay between thought and emotion, both for ourselves and when interacting with others.  When our emotions are appropriately expressed and balanced, we make better decisions, our problem solving abilities improve, and we can cope with change and life’s challenges more effectively.  My EQ leads you through a practical five step process to help you increase self awareness and social awareness, improving self management and enhancing your relationship management skills.</p>', 3, '2011-09-20 02:59:02', '2012-05-20 11:33:56'),
(45, 6, 'Health Check-In', '<p><img src="/system/images/BAhbBlsHOgZmSSIvMjAxMS8xMC8yOC8xM18wOV81MF84OTJfaGVhbHRoX2NoZWNraW4ucG5nBjoGRVQ/health_checkin.png" title="Health Checkin" alt="Health Checkin" rel="225x255" height="386" width="634" />The personal Health Check In allows you to record your energy, stress and comfort levels and to monitor how these are changing over time.  You can use this to gauge your progress.</p>', 4, '2011-09-20 02:59:02', '2012-05-20 11:33:56'),
(46, 6, 'Timed Reminders', '<p>The Timed Reminder allows you to set a customised alert to remind you to use the program, drink water or take a break.  Alternatively you can create your own personal reminder.</p>\r\n<p><img src="/images/pages/features/reminder_screenshot.jpg" alt="Reminder Emails Screenshot" /></p>', 5, '2011-09-20 02:59:02', '2012-05-20 11:33:56'),
