(83, 22, 'Right Content', '<h2>My 5 reflects the expertise of a wide range of skilled practitioners</h2>\r\n<p>This expertise covers a variety of approaches to natural health and wellness.  We have synthesized their approaches to wellness to give you a dynamic health program that infuses the latest fitness concepts from the West with the ancient arts of the East.</p>', 1, '2011-10-20 07:06:23', '2011-10-24 23:11:53'),
(84, 21, 'Right Content', '<h2>We are passionate in our desire to deliver products and solutions that are simple and practical and that really work, reflected in our values:</h2>\r\n<ul><li>    <strong>Inspire</strong> and motivate you to seek improvement in your physical, mental and emotional wellbeing</li>\r\n<li><strong>Empower </strong>you to make changes, through giving you the tools you need to have a real impact on how you feel</li>\r\n<li><strong>Re-energise </strong>you through transporting you to an invigorating environment that re-energises and recharges</li>\r\n<li><strong>Deliver </strong>you simple and effective answers to common health issues, drawing on both Eastern and Western perspectives</li>\r\n<li>Benefits that e<strong>ndure</strong>, offering lasting results</li>\r\n</ul>', 1, '2011-10-20 07:07:36', '2012-03-01 09:18:20'),
(85, 26, 'Right Content', '<h2>My body... My life... My 5</h2>\r\n<p>Our vision embodies our commitment to helping you get more out of your life – both at work and at play.&#160;  Long hours spent sitting or using a computer can place a significant strain on your body.  We know this, and look to offer you welcome respite for mind and body.</p>\r\n<p>My 5 ''s mission is to empower each individual to manage their own health and wellbeing.  In particular, My 5 offers:</p>\r\n<ul><li>    Products</li>\r\n<li>Services</li>\r\n<li>Education and information</li>\r\n<li>Inspiration and motivation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>All of these are designed to help you enhance your health and wellbeing.</p>', 1, '2011-10-20 07:08:14', '2011-10-24 23:11:07'),
