(92, 34, 'Body', '<h2>Seminars</h2>\r\n\r\n<p class="text-align-left">My 5 offers a variety of ways to support the wellbeing culture within your organisation by providing a wide range of seminars facilitated by a team of accredited health professionals.</p>\r\n<p>The seminars can be packaged in a flexible offering alongside the My 5 on line wellbeing program to offer you a truly holistic workplace wellbeing program.</p>\r\n<p>Our range of seminars can be specifically tailored to suit your needs. We offer:</p>\r\n<ul><li>Stretching and posture for the workplace</li>\r\n<li>Back and spine care</li>\r\n<li>Meditation and relaxation</li>\r\n<li>Nutrition and healthy eating at work</li>\r\n<li>Self-massage</li>\r\n<li>Tai chi and yoga</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>We will continue to support your workforce with regular newsletters and health tips relevant to the workplace environment.</p>\r\n<h2>Assessments&#160;&#160;&#160;</h2>\r\n<p>My 5 in association with <a target="_blank" title="http://www.wellnessteam.com.au" href="http://www.wellnessteam.com.au">Wellness Team</a> can offer health assessments utilizing innovative technology that engages your employees and helps them increase their own health awareness whilst taking more responsibility for their own health.</p>\r\n<p>The BioPhotonic Scanner utilises unique and patented Nobel Prize winning technology. It provides an innovative way to measure the carotenoid antioxidant levels in the body, giving you an indicator of your immune system''s health and ability to combat illness. It does this accurately and non-invasively in 90 seconds, with no needles, no pain and no stress.</p>\r\n<p>The scanner will provide you with a scientifically validated measurement of how well your diet, exercise and lifestyle are protecting your bodies'' cells and your overall health.</p>\r\n<p>Each employee receives an explanatory booklet and a scan card which records their score.</p>\r\n<p><img class="image-align-right" rel="225x255" alt="Wellness Team" title="Wellness Team" src="http://my5.com.au/system/images/BAhbB1sHOgZmSSIuMjAxMi8wMy8wNi8xMF8zMF8xNV8yMjZfV2VsbG5lc3NfVGVhbS5qcGcGOgZFVFsIOgZwOgp0aHVtYkkiDTIyNXgyNTU+BjsGVA/Wellness%20Team.jpg" height="56" width="225" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Massage</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><br />We provide professional massage therapists with specialist ergonomic chairs and head rests to give a fully clothed neck and shoulder massage.My 5 in association with <a target="_blank" title="http://www.corporatebodies.com" href="http://www.corporatebodies.com">Corporate Bodies</a> offer a comprehensive workplace massage service. Massage is a great way to re-energise your employees without having to leave their desks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Massages can last from 5 to 30 minutes depending on your requirements and can be performed at the desk or in a specified room.</p>\r\n<p>Massage can help to:</p>\r\n<ul><li>Reduce stress</li>\r\n<li>Release muscular tension and pain&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; </li>\r\n<li>Help increase motivation and performance levels</li>\r\n<li>Help your employees to feel re-energised and refocused</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>How does it work?</p>\r\n<p>We will come to your business location. We offer an on line booking system with flexible scheduling options.</p>\r\n<h2><a target="_blank" title="http://www.corporatebodies.com/" href="http://www.corporatebodies.com/"><img class="image-align-right" rel="225x255" alt="Corporate Bodies" title="Corporate Bodies" src="/system/images/BAhbB1sHOgZmSSIxMjAxMi8wMy8wNS8xN18xMF80OV8xMjJfQ29ycG9yYXRlX0JvZGllcy5qcGcGOgZFVFsIOgZwOgp0aHVtYkkiDTIyNXgyNTU+BjsGVA/Corporate%20Bodies.jpg" height="47" width="225" /></a>\r\n</h2>\r\n', 0, '2012-02-29 00:04:23', '2012-03-12 05:14:12'),
